    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><div class=\"float-clear\"></div><div><div class=\"rd__wrp-image relative\">\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/5etools-mirror-2/5etools-img/main/bestiary/ToB1-2023/Elder Shadow Drake.webp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n\t\t\t\t<img class=\"rd__image\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/5etools-mirror-2/5etools-img/main/bestiary/ToB1-2023/Elder Shadow Drake.webp\" />\n\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t</div></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p><i>A large dragon with black scales and shadowy wings emerges from the darkness. Its red eyes glare bright as coals, and it speaks in a deep monotone.</i></p><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"1\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Solitary Lairs.</span></span> <p>They haunt dark and lonely places, such as deep caves, dense forests, shadowy ruins, and many wild locations in the Plane of Shadow. They are long-lived for drakes, often reaching 250 years of age, and mate rarely, abandoning their eggs shortly before hatching.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"2\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Fade Into Shadows.</span></span> <p>An elder shadow drake naturally fades from view in areas of dim light or darkness, becoming invisible until it attacks or is bathed in sunlight.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div></div></div>",
        "public": ""
